---
title: "US38 — Customise plan parameters"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>PlanDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>RegeneratePlan
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>AiGateway + SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: change duration / frequency / preferences
  B->>C: regenerate(options)
  C->>G: suggest-plan with constraints
  G-->>C: revised plan
  C-->>B: updated fitness_plan (regenerated_count+1)
  B-->>A: plan reflects custom parameters
